      "text": "fe_report.json        top_ids, disc_ids, top_ngrams\nfeature_scaler.joblib RobustScaler(p1..p99)\niforest.joblib        IsolationForest(n=300, c=0.02)\nvae_encoder.weights.h5  latent_dim=8, Dense(32,SELU)\nvae_decoder.weights.h5  Dropout(0.2)\nresults.json          threshold = -0.0132",
